## üì• Download the Executable

You can download the executable from the following link:

- [Download the FileManager Executable](https://github.com/khadimFaye/DartProjects/tree/master/FileManager/filemanager.exe)

## üîß Requirements

To run FileManager, you will need:

- **Windows 7 or later**
- **PowerShell**
- **Chocolatey** (for managing packages on Windows)
- **Dart SDK** (to compile or run the Dart source code)

### üõ†Ô∏è How to Run the Code
